    {
      "text": "這件上衣有沒有白色的？",
      "pinyin": "Zhè jiàn shàngyī yǒu méiyǒu báisè de?",
      "pinyin_numeric": "zhe4 jian4 shang4yi1 you3 mei2you3 bai2se4 de0",
      "translation_en": "Do you have this top in white?",
